personnes simples, des méthodes simples visant à simplifier au maximum\r\nles processus pour faire les produits les plus simples pour nos clients\r\n\r\n<strong>\" La simplicité est la sophistication suprême \"\r\n</strong>-<em> Léonard de Vinci</em>'),(20116,1070,'_section_0_contenu','field_5734867d2894d'),(20117,1070,'section_0_action-title',''),(20118,1070,'_section_0_action-title','field_573486992894e'),(20119,1070,'section_0_action-link',''),(20120,1070,'_section_0_action-link','field_573486d22894f'),(20121,1070,'section_0_media','image'),(20122,1070,'_section_0_media','field_573486f228950'),(20123,1070,'section_0_media-img','1029'),(20124,1070,'_section_0_media-img','field_5734871228951'),(20125,1070,'section_0_media-video',''),(20126,1070,'_section_0_media-video','field_5734874d28952'),(20127,1070,'section_1_title','P pour Plaisir '),(20128,1070,'_section_1_title','field_5734865c2894c'),(20129,1070,'section_1_contenu','&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nNotre équipe est chez Cedreo aussi et surtout pour se faire PLAISIR, une notion t<span style=\"font-size: inherit; line-height: 1.6;\">rop souvent délaissée dans l\'économie moderne.\r\nChez nous cela est essentiel à la fois pour nos équipes mais aussi pour nos clients qui doivent prendre PLAISIR à travailler avec nous !</span>\r\n\r\n<strong>\" Ce que je sais faire de mieux, c\'est partager mon enthousiasme \"</strong>\r\n- <em>Bill Gates</em>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),(20130,1070,'_section_1_contenu','field_5734867d2894d'),(20131,1070,'section_1_action-title',''),(20132,1070,'_section_1_action-title','field_573486992894e'),(20133,1070,'section_1_action-link',''),(20134,1070,'_section_1_action-link','field_573486d22894f'),(20135,1070,'section_1_media','image'),(20136,1070,'_section_1_media','field_573486f228950'),(20137,1070,'section_1_media-img','1025'),(20138,1070,'_section_1_media-img','field_5734871228951'),(20139,1070,'section_1_media-video',''),(20140,1070,'_section_1_media-video','field_5734874d28952'),(20141,1070,'section_2_title','E pour Ethique '),(20142,1070,'_section_2_title','field_5734865c2894c'),(20143,1070,'section_2_contenu','&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nLe respect de la parole est essentiel et dans les deux sens.\r\nCela semble évident mais nous jugeons qu\'il est toujours utile de le rappeler !\r\n\r\n<strong>\" Les deux choses les plus importantes n\'apparaissent\r\npas au bilan d\'une entreprise : sa réputation et ses Hommes \"</strong>\r\n- <em>Henry Ford</em>'),(20144,1070,'_section_2_contenu','field_5734867d2894d'),(20145,1070,'section_2_action-title',''),(20146,1070,'_section_2_action-title','field_573486992894e'),(20147,1070,'section_2_action-link',''),(20148,1070,'_section_2_action-link','field_573486d22894f'),(20149,1070,'section_2_media','image'),(20150,1070,'_section_2_media','field_573486f228950'),(20151,1070,'section_2_media-img','1045'),(20152,1070,'_section_2_media-img','field_5734871228951'),(20153,1070,'section_2_media-video',''),(20154,1070,'_section_2_media-video','field_5734874d28952'),(20155,1070,'section_3_title','A pour Audace '),(20156,1070,'_section_3_title','field_5734865c2894c'),(20157,1070,'section_3_contenu','&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nNous sommes convaincus qu\'il est nécessaire de prendre des risques pour innover.\r\nCedreo investit chaque année plus de 25% de son CA en R&amp;D.\r\n\r\n<strong>\" Une personne qui n\'a jamais commis d\'erreur n\'a jamais innové \"\r\n</strong>- <em>Albert Einstein</em>'),(20158,1070,'_section_3_contenu','field_5734867d2894d'),(20159,1070,'section_3_action-title',''),(20160,1070,'_section_3_action-title','field_573486992894e'),(20161,1070,'section_3_action-link',''),(20162,1070,'_section_3_action-link','field_573486d22894f'),(20163,1070,'section_3_media','image'),(20164,1070,'_section_3_media','field_573486f228950'),(20165,1070,'section_3_media-img','1040'),(20166,1070,'_section_3_media-img','field_5734871228951'),(20167,1070,'section_3_media-video',''),(20168,1070,'_section_3_media-video','field_5734874d2